{"tid":1578291,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE倒數5天回歸！ Mina緊牽媽媽手返韓…團體照「站正中央｣成員緊依靠","createTime":"2019-09-18T05:43:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T01:26:08.000Z","uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3972f045cd8a3bf8a1aa4bdfa124c7c3d33f35ba","tid":1578291,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:43:12.000Z","msg":"韓團TWICE將在23日以新歌《FEELING SPECIAL》回歸，引人注目的除了這次全新造型風格，還有因恐慌症所苦的Mina動向。而她在回歸SHOWCASE前於17日返韓，在台灣時間17日23點曝光的團體照中可以看見以她為中心，也能看成是對外傳遞彼此永不放手的堅定情感。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4377/d4377336.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4377%2Fd4377336.jpg&h=99570053&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Mina（左二）即使為恐慌症所苦仍和成員們一起拍攝回歸MV。（圖／翻攝自TWICE臉書）<br />\n<br />\nTWICE這次以《FEELING SPECIAL》回歸樂壇，大部分成員都將頭髮改成大旁分，妝感也變得更加成熟美艷，每日推出不同成員的20秒TEASER影片都讓外界讚嘆「美麗沒有極限」，再5天她們將舉辦SHOWCASE正式對外展現舞台，結束和家人一起過節的外國成員們也紛紛回到南韓。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4377/4377337.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4377%2F4377337.jpg&h=91147d3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Mina於17日回到南韓。（圖／翻攝自studio PARN YouTube）<br />\n<br />\nMina就在18日現身金溥機場，一身全白裝扮搭配白色運動帽、白色口罩，與上次抵韓全程低頭顫抖的模樣很不相同，還能抬頭看一下前來的媒體，在台灣時間17日23點曝光的團體照中，其他8名成員以她為中心緊緊依靠的模樣，讓粉絲看了深受感動。<br />\n<br />\n►媽媽比女兒還正！全靠「超強神器」辦到<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4377/d4377335.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4377%2Fd4377335.jpg&h=17d807b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲TWICE新歌團體照曝光。（圖／翻攝自TWICE臉書）"},{"pid":"5de95aaada443c26a608b5ec04cfcb324adcc5f3","tid":1578291,"uid":54631,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:50:36.000Z","msg":"「媽媽比女兒還正！」<br />\n啫係生咗個女？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b96b11424943b41ecd89793060a11c6b81cde6d0","tid":1578291,"uid":37146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:56:32.000Z","msg":"話時話<br />\n如果有得同南南曳曳但要搭埋佢老母<br />\n有冇人制<br />\n利申：狗衝"},{"pid":"bf5b660592e1bfb4225032af1875aedb45d6555c","tid":1578291,"uid":270909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T19:52:32.000Z","msg":"我認唔到西女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 揾咗陣先見到"},{"pid":"a9f6499a2ec7cb437b40a863f75944ded3136c87","tid":1578291,"uid":149371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b96b11424943b41ecd89793060a11c6b81cde6d0","tid":1578291,"uid":37146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:56:32.000Z","msg":"話時話<br />\n如果有得同南南曳曳但要搭埋佢老母<br />\n有冇人制<br />\n利申：狗衝"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T01:26:08.000Z","msg":"我會滿足外母先<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}